{"tid":1428272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方：浸大生涉藏高能量「鐳射槍」可致視網膜永久損害","createTime":"2019-08-07T09:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:36:21.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a2673620865279bbcb35b1473369889960cd9d8c","tid":1428272,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190807_20190807-162254.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190807_20190807-162254.jpg&h=9bdb9186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浸大學生會會長方仲賢買觀星筆後，被指涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器被捕。有組織罪案及三合會調查科高級警司李桂華表示，涉事物件並非鐳射筆，是高能量的「鐳射槍」，擔心可令視網膜永久損害。<br />\n<br />\n李桂華指出，鐳射光線會阻礙警方工作，不少同已事因此受傷，警方已諮詢眼科醫生意見，為警員加配護目鏡，否則可導致出現「閃盲」現象。他重申，不要將鐳射光射眼，可導致永久失明。<br />\n<br />\n警方在記者會上，即場示範經鐳射光照射後的情況。現場一名戴上黑色眼鏡人員，手持銀色筆狀物件，在較近距離照射紙張，大約十秒，紙張上出現白煙。李桂華指，用作示範的物件，屬證物之一。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，昨晚約7時半，有休班警員發現一名男子在排檔問強力「鐳射槍」，形跡可疑並企圖逃跑，警員成功阻止，在男子隨身袋內找到十支鐳射槍，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器，將男子拘捕。"},{"pid":"a904c951040752bd16739c84de31a7bdedaa2b42","tid":1428272,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:18:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473268-20190807.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473268-20190807.htm&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=6a669fbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473268-20190807.htm&h=6802e3bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473268-20190807.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f1fdd3b9778c84d24d9072ca408bf9ff1c64a6de","tid":1428272,"uid":5290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:19:47.000Z","msg":"用黑警嘅視網膜嚟測試下先啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fd73a6d05f96dde939c91d221f3b648738a6a3","tid":1428272,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:22:01.000Z","msg":"槍？？大炮啊笨？屈得就屈"},{"pid":"1b0d32021f708b488d5a2d2a75eee789a0af7a20","tid":1428272,"uid":282359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:39:54.000Z","msg":"都係果句。<br />\n有狗盲未？有狗真係永久失明先同我講嘢啦。"},{"pid":"639570dbba5dc1d1226d3989aaa9cf1e56affe12","tid":1428272,"uid":286705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"比班美國人睇到 實笑死"},{"pid":"26646414c22915176fe0eba594c3ca2f0fee4a82","tid":1428272,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"639570dbba5dc1d1226d3989aaa9cf1e56affe12","tid":1428272,"uid":286705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"比班美國人睇到 實笑死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"之前胸部襲警已經上左國際頭條笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64be1e870ffbb1eb14abf358b7dd1854a1e86dd","tid":1428272,"uid":16066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:36:21.000Z","msg":"我用拳頭塞入去汪汪既屁屁<br />\n會永久性容易失禁添啊<br />\n你唔拉哂全部香港人？"}]}